  "prompt": "I told her I like her, now what?",
  "response": "It sounds like you've taken a brave step by expressing your feelings! Here are some potential next steps you can consider:\n\n1. **Give Her Space**: If she needs time to process your feelings, give her some space. Everyone reacts differently to such revelations.\n\n2. **Communicate Openly**: If she responds positively, have an open conversation about your feelings and what they mean for both of you moving forward.\n\n3. **Gauge Her Response**: Pay attention to her reaction\u2014if she seems receptive, you can discuss how to take things further. If she doesn\u2019t feel the same way, be respectful of her feelings.\n\n4. **Plan Your Next Move**: Depending on her response, you could suggest spending more time together, whether as friends or in a more romantic context.\n\n5. **Be Honest**: If she feels the same way, be open about what you're both looking for in a relationship.\n\n6. **Be Prepared for Any Outcome**: Understand that she may not feel the same way. If that's the case, try to handle it gracefully and maintain your friendship if possible.\n\nRemember, the key is to communicate openly and respectfully, regardless of her response. Good luck!",
